s.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The theme\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1322}, {\"ngram\": \"some very creative entries\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"the junior school\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1382}, {\"ngram\": \"its arts\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"photography\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"green-screen entries\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Senior leaders also became \\\"mystery readers\\\" - they would read a story over the school's intercom in a \\\"mysterious voice\\\" and all the students would try to guess their identify, with correct guesses going into a draw for a prize box.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Senior leaders\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"mystery readers\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the school's intercom\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1565}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"mysterious voice\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"all the students\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"their identify\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"correct guesses\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"a draw\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"a prize box\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When the mystery reader gets announced later in the day, their excitement is real.\\\"\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mystery reader\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"their excitement\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leah says the school had a \\\"dress up in black\\\" day to support Team New Zealand and \\\"Mascots 'n Milos\\\", for which children could create their own mascots and enjoy reading stories with them with a Milo outside in the fresh air.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah\", \"score\": 0.9964725283316911, \"rank\": 0.003241428727091673, \"text\": \"Leah\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah\"}, {\"begin\": 1851, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 0.9999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.489777538322692e-12, \"text\": \"Team New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_New_Zealand\"}, {\"begin\": 1985, \"end\": 1989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\", \"score\": 0.9992346355814815, \"rank\": 0.0007659506490037383, \"text\": \"Milo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Titus_Annius_Milo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the school\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"dress\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"black\\\" day\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Mascots 'n Milos\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"their own mascots\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"the fresh air\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2014}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The students also had an Olympic reading challenge card to complete over the week with various reading challenges and everyone was encouraged to dress up for the book character parade.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The students\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic reading challenge card\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2072